<h1>Find a File </h1>

Search for a file in the <b>earth</b> database.(* can be used as a wildcard, eg *.rb)
<br />
<br />
<% form_tag :action => 'find' do %>
  Filename:     <%= text_field_tag 'filename' %><br>
  Owned by:     <%= text_field_tag 'user' %><br>
  Bigger than:  <%= text_field_tag 'size' %> bytes<br>
  <%= submit_tag 'Find' %>
<% end %>

